n-drenched Parisian living room with worn wooden floorboards and tall arched windows\"\nKamera: lens + diyafram + açı + framing. \"shot on a 50mm lens at f/2.8, eye-level medium shot...\"\nIşık: yön + sıcaklık + sertlik. \"Soft golden hour light from a window off-camera left in warm 3200K\"\n\nZorunlu içerik checklist'i\nParagrafın içinde şunlar mutlaka olacak. Bir madde eksikse paragrafı yeniden yaz:\n\nKarakterin somut fiziksel tanımı\nKarakterin pozu/aksiyonu\nMekân\nLens mm değeri\nDiyafram f değeri\nKamera açısı (eye-level, low angle vb.) + framing (medium shot, wide vb.)\nIşığın yönü\nIşığın Kelvin sıcaklığı\n","Evin balkonundan bana bakan bir kedi sadece kafası ve gövdesi gözüküyor, beyaz tüyleri ve sarı çizgileri var",false,false,"text"]},{"id":44,"type":"StringConcatenate","pos":[-1561.813053313151,-1097.750523927296],"size":[420.7963920830998,203.80259834258038],"flags":{},"order":2,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"string_a","name":"string_a","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"string_a"},"link":58},{"localized_name":"string_b","name":"string_b","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"string_b"},"link":43},{"localized_name":"delimiter","name":"delimiter","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"delimiter"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"STRING","name":"STRING","type":"STRING","links":[44]}],"title":"Extra Prompt","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.22.2","Node name for S&R":"StringConcatenate"},"widgets_values":["","",""]}],"groups":[],"links":[{"id":16,"origin_id":20,"origin_slot":0,"target_id":19,"target_slot":0,"type":"OLLAMA_CONNECTIVITY"},{"id":43,"origin_id":19,"origin_slot":0,"target_id":44,"target_slot":1,"type":"STRING"},{"id":44,"origin_id":44,"origin_slot":0,"target_id":-20,"target_slot":0,"type":"STRING"},{"id":51,"origin_id":-10,"origin_slot":0,"target_id":20,"target_slot":0,"type":"STRING"},{"id":53,"origin_id":-10,"origin_slot":1,"target_id":20,"target_slot":1,"type":"COMBO"},{"id":54,"origin_id":-10,"origin_slot":2,"target_id":1